    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="搭建简易的Blog"><a href="#搭建简易的Blog" class="headerlink" title="搭建简易的Blog"></a>搭建简易的Blog</h1><span id="more"></span><h2 id="1-环境"><a href="#1-环境" class="headerlink" title="1. 环境"></a>1. 环境</h2><ol><li><strong>node.js</strong></li></ol><h2 id="2-安装hexo"><a href="#2-安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装hexo"></a>2. 安装hexo</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-建站"><a href="#3-建站" class="headerlink" title="3. 建站"></a>3. 建站</h2><ol><li>初始化本地仓库  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init [文件名称]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>下载依赖<br>根据提示，前往[文件名称]目录下，下载依赖  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 提交到git仓库的插件(遇到error:not git时)</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>启动项目<br>此时项目已经创建好，在目录中找到<code>_config.yml</code>文件，滑到最后找到并修改  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Deployment</span><br><span class="line">## Docs: https:<span class="comment">//hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: 你的仓库SSH地址</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master(github默认分支为main,gitee为master，自行修改)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>清除、生成、上传<br>完成以上以上步骤，Blog则已经创建完成，执行如下的：<font color="red">清除、生成、上传</font>命令  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 清除缓存</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 生成页面</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 上传更新到git仓库中</span><br><span class="line"># 注意：这一步必须要执行下载依赖中的第二条命令</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
